        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine your<strong> carrot & cabbage slaw mix</strong> with <strong>half </strong>your <strong>mayo</strong>, <strong>half </strong>your <strong>white wine vinegar</strong> (you’ll use the rest later!) and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> – this is your<strong> slaw</strong></p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Combine the<strong> remaining mayo </strong>and <strong>white wine vinegar </strong>with the<strong> chopped garlic </strong>(not a big garlic fan? Try using less!) – this is your <strong>garlic mayo</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
